                    <p><h3>At  <b>AlperKayali</b>,  we are committed to providing a safe and healthy work environment for all employees and to minimizing the environmental impact of our operations. Our Occupational Safety and Environmental Policy outlines our commitment to maintaining the highest standards of occupational health and safety and environmental management.</h3></p>


